N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1275.4 - Enplaning or deplaning passengers restricted

State Regulations

Passengers shall not be permitted to enplane or deplane
except in the presence of authorized personnel of the aircraft
operator. Notes
